<div id="intro">
<p>Darcs is a free and open source, cross-platform version control system, like <a href="http://git-scm.com/">git</a>, <a href="http://mercurial.selenic.com/">mercurial</a> or <a href="http://subversion.apache.org/">svn</a> but with a very different approach: focus on changes rather than snapshots. Darcs offers a <strong>freer</strong> way of working, and a <strong>simpler</strong> user interface. Darcs <em>does not require a central server</em>, and work perfectly in <strong>offline</strong> mode.</p>
